A SkyWest Airlines pilot plunged a plane carrying 75 passengers into a terrifying dive on Wednesday after a reported loss of cabin pressure in mid-air .
Frightened passengers held their heads and prayed as Flight 5622 , operating as a United Express , dropped nearly 30,000 feet in eight minutes and made an emergency landing in Buffalo , New York .
